---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const page_title = "Cookie Policy";
const page_description = "Information on the use of cookies on privacy-crypto.com.";
---

<Layout title={page_title} description={page_description} maxWidth="max-w-3xl" lang="en">
  <header class="mb-8 border-b border-white/[0.05] pb-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 text-white">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">Last updated: May 2026</p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none">
    <div class="bento-card p-6 border border-white/[0.05] bg-white/[0.02]">
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
            This website uses cookies and similar technologies to ensure the proper functioning of its features and to improve the browsing experience, while respecting user privacy.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">1. Strictly Necessary Technical Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
            We exclusively use technical cookies necessary for the basic operation of the site. For example, we locally store your preference regarding the visual theme (light mode / dark mode). This data remains on your device and is not transmitted to us or to third parties. These cookies do not require prior user consent.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">2. Analytics and Third-Party Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
            For website statistics, we use <strong>Umami Analytics</strong>, a privacy-friendly and open-source solution specifically designed to comply with the GDPR without the need for tracking cookies. Umami does not collect personal data, does not track users across different websites, and all collected data is fully anonymized and aggregated. 
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">3. How to Manage Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
            Since we only use strictly necessary cookies, no consent banner is displayed. You can, however, configure your web browser to reject all cookies. Please note that disabling local technical cookies will cause your dark/light theme preference to be lost on every page reload.
        </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
